# SCSS Standards

## Design Tokens

| Requirement              | Details                                               |
| ------------------------ | ----------------------------------------------------- |
| **Use design tokens**    | Colors from `--color-*`, spacing from `--spacing-*`   |
| **No hardcoded colors**  | Always use CSS custom properties                      |
| **No hardcoded spacing** | Use `--spacing-*` tokens                              |

## Focus & Interaction States

| Requirement        | Details                                               |
| ------------------ | ----------------------------------------------------- |
| **Focus states**   | Use `[data-focus-visible]` for keyboard-only outlines |
| **Hover states**   | Use `&:hover` with appropriate token colors           |
| **Disabled states** | Use `[data-disabled]` or `&:disabled`                |

## CSS Modules

| Requirement          | Details                                       |
| -------------------- | --------------------------------------------- |
| **Avoid `:global`**  | CSS modules should stay scoped                |
| **Use `classnames`** | Not template literals for conditional classes |

## Code Style

| Requirement                | Details                                       |
| -------------------------- | ----------------------------------------------|
| **Use mixins**             | Extract repeated patterns                     |
| **Pill border-radius**     | Use `9999px` for safety                       |
| **Pseudo-element order**   | Put `content: ''` first                       |
| **Logical property order** | Position → Box model → Visual                 |
| **Do not use comments**    | Only for complex constructions, to explain    |

## Storybook Styles

| Requirement                     | Details                         |
| ------------------------------- | ------------------------------- |
| **No inline styles in stories** | Move to `*.stories.module.scss` |

## Examples

```scss
// Good
.button {
  color: var(--color-text-primary);
  padding: var(--spacing-2) var(--spacing-4);
  border-radius: var(--radius-md);

  &:hover {
    background-color: var(--color-bg-hover);
  }

  &[data-focus-visible] {
    outline: 2px solid var(--color-focus);
    outline-offset: 2px;
  }

  &[data-disabled] {
    opacity: 0.5;
    cursor: not-allowed;
  }
}

.pill {
  border-radius: 9999px; // Safe pill radius
}

.icon::before {
  content: ''; // content first in pseudo-elements
  display: block;
  width: 16px;
  height: 16px;
}
```

```scss
// Bad
.button {
  color: #333; // hardcoded color
  padding: 8px 16px; // hardcoded spacing

  &:focus {
    // should use [data-focus-visible]
    outline: 2px solid blue; // hardcoded color
  }
}

:global(.external-class) {
  // avoid :global, keep modules scoped
}
```
